<a href="https://github.com/pieterderycke/PhotoWall"><img style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_darkblue_121621.png" alt="Fork me on GitHub"></a>

<h2 class="cameraIcon">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
<p>This is a photo wall example using HTML5 technologies. Every minute, this web application uses the web cam to take a picture of the user. The photos of all the users are shared on this wall.</p>
<p>At the moment of writing, this sample only works in <b>Google Chrome 20+.</b></p>
